hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 费米-狄拉克积分及其在一般 $\eta$ 处的导数：
$$F_{1/2}(\eta)=\frac1{\Gamma(3/2)}\int_0^\infty\frac{x^{1/2}}{e^{x-\eta}+1}\,dx,$$
$$\frac{dF_{1/2}}{d\eta}
=\frac1{\Gamma(3/2)}\int_0^\infty x^{1/2}\frac{\partial}{\partial\eta}\Bigl(\frac1{e^{x-\eta}+1}\Bigr)\,dx
=\frac1{\Gamma(3/2)}\int_0^\infty x^{1/2}\frac{e^{x-\eta}}{(e^{x-\eta}+1)^2}\,dx.$$

2. 在 $\eta=0$ 处求值并使用级数
$$\frac{e^x}{(e^x+1)^2}
=\sum_{k=1}^\infty(-1)^{k+1}k\,e^{-kx}.$$
因此
$$\left.\frac{dF_{1/2}}{d\eta}\right|_{\eta=0}
=\frac1{\Gamma(3/2)}\sum_{k=1}^\infty(-1)^{k+1}k\int_0^\infty x^{1/2}e^{-kx}\,dx.$$

3. 使用 $\int_0^\infty x^{1/2}e^{-kx}dx=\Gamma(3/2)/k^{3/2}$，所以
$$\left.\frac{dF_{1/2}}{d\eta}\right|_{\eta=0}
=\sum_{k=1}^\infty(-1)^{k+1}k\frac{\Gamma(3/2)}{\Gamma(3/2)\,k^{3/2}}
=\sum_{k=1}^\infty(-1)^{k+1}k^{-1/2}
=\eta\bigl(\tfrac12\bigr).$$

4. 将其与狄利克雷eta函数和zeta函数关联：
$$\eta\bigl(\tfrac12\bigr)=(1-2^{1-\tfrac12})\,\zeta\bigl(\tfrac12\bigr)
=(1-\sqrt2)\,\zeta\bigl(\tfrac12\bigr).$$
